294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d16233b470d8e0b336133c14beb58eda03ba530","tid":1867909,"uid":346655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"就咁為考試，其實係無問題，但考級其實好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你唔係要用張cert黎證明啲咩，不如慢慢學好過。<br />\n<br />\n太快考曬級會令你以為自己好勁，但其實有啲技巧會淨係識用係首考試曲度，反而唔識變通用落其他曲度。"},{"pid":"4d9ab9429c947fc4d2ee0185c3b4b5f88d24a235","tid":1867909,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"鋼琴唔止得古典<br />\n做到隨心所欲，心諗乜就彈乜先係極致(好唔好聽又係另一個問題）<br />\n例如以下咁，身邊啲朋友由細學到大，考埋八級都話呢啲唔識彈<br />\n所以睇你追求彈到人哋嘅歌就滿足，定係其他<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nsn8ZGb80-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNsn8ZGb80-g&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwSRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=dbaf64d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nsn8ZGb80-g</a>"}]}